{"tid":50649,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[offical]柏祖被炒","createTime":"2016-12-22T15:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T15:21:34.000Z","uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9110db17e9fac7baea5176975ba7b24610b164b2","tid":50649,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:08:35.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://www.cpfc.co.uk/news/article/2016-17/club-statement-cpfc-3482525.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cpfc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F2016-17%2Fclub-statement-cpfc-3482525.aspx&d=c9o%2Bp0wmVt%2Bykjwp0NVuh4scwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=850d890d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cpfc.co.uk/news/article/2016-17/club-statement-cpfc-3482525.aspx</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\nPUBLISHED<br />\n<br />\n14:51 22nd December 2016<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nClub Statement &ndash; 22nd December 2016<br />\n<br />\nCrystal Palace F.C. have today asked Alan Pardew to step down as Manager of the Club.<br />\n <br />\nClub Chairman Steve Parish said, &ldquo;I would like to put on record our sincere gratitude for the tremendous service Alan has given us, both in his time here as Manager and previously as a player.  Following a fantastic second half of 2014/15, the 2015/16 season culminated in only narrowly missing out on winning the FA cup as well as securing our Premier League place for a record breaking fourth time. During his tenure Alan&rsquo;s hard work and dedication were without question, he has improved so many areas of the Club and we wish him the very best for the future.<br />\n <br />\nWith games now coming thick and fast over the holiday period the Club are hoping to put someone in place as quickly as possible but have nothing to say about a replacement at this time.<br />\n<br />\nRead more at <a href=\"http://www.cpfc.co.uk/news/article/2016-17/club-statement-cpfc-3482525.aspx#WPcoVMoHM2H93FvP.99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cpfc.co.uk%2